lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur's charge towards their first English top-flight title since 1961 hit a speed bump on Wednesday with a 1-0 Premier League defeat at West Ham United.

headline.print_headline: Tottenham's Title Bid Runs Into Trouble at West Ham
